                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-368-18640229 t18640229-368-punishment-61"></join>Confined Nine Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
